(rf/reg-event-db
  :data/set-search-value
  (fn [db [_ val]]
    (println :data/set-search-value val)
    (-> db
        (assoc-in [:data :search-value] val)
        (assoc-in [:data :search-updating?] false))))


(rf/reg-event-db
  :data/set-tmp-search-value
  (fn [db [_ val]]
    (let [bp (get-in db [:window :breakpoint])
          md>=? (#{:md :lg :xl} bp)]
      (when-let [old-timeout (get-in db [:data :sync-timeout])]
        (e/tf-cancel! old-timeout))
      (let [timeout (when md>=? (e/after-timeout 1500 (rf/dispatch [:data/set-search-value val])))]
        (-> db
            (assoc-in [:data :tmp-search-value] val)
            (assoc-in [:data :sync-timeout] timeout)
            (assoc-in [:data :search-updating?] md>=?)
            )))))

                  :min-pace   (get-in db [:data :settings :min-pace])

      {:ws/send {:event  :data/make-market-order
                 :params params}})))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :data/change-market-order-qty
  (fn [{db :db} [_ id qty]]
    (when-let [old-timeout (get-in db [:data :sync-timeout])]
      (e/tf-cancel! old-timeout))
    (cond
      (str/empty-or-nil? qty)
      (let [event {:event  :data/change-market-order-qty
                   :params [id 0]}
            timeout (e/after-timeout 3000 (rf/dispatch [:ws/send event]))]
        {:db (->> db
                  (sp/setval [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :order] 0)
                  (sp/setval [:data :sync-timeout] timeout))})
      (not (neg? qty))
      (let [event {:event  :data/change-market-order-qty
                   :params [id (js/parseFloat qty)]}
            timeout (e/after-timeout 3000 (rf/dispatch [:ws/send event]))]
        {:db (->> db
                  (sp/setval [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :order] (js/parseFloat qty))
                  (sp/setval [:data :sync-timeout] timeout))}))))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :data/change-market-order-supply-days
  (fn [{db :db} [_ id days]]
    (when-let [old-timeout (get-in db [:data :sync-timeout])]
      (e/tf-cancel! old-timeout))
    (let [qty (sp/select-one [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :qty] db)
          old-order (sp/select-one [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :order] db)
          pace (sp/select-one [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :pace] db)
          old-days (e/round0 (/ old-order pace))
          order (if (> days old-days)
                  (max (inc old-order) (Math/ceil (* pace days)))
                  (min (dec old-order) (Math/ceil (* pace days))))
          order (max 0 (- order (max 0 qty)))
          event {:event  :data/change-market-order-qty
                 :params [id order]}
          timeout (e/after-timeout 3000 (rf/dispatch [:ws/send event]))]
      {:db (->> db
                (sp/setval [:data :market-order sp/ALL #(= id (:id %)) :order] order)
                (sp/setval [:data :sync-timeout] timeout))})))
